    "description": {
      "value": "<p>@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.WklldBUUO3oesibI]{UM5 Ch.6: Granades &amp; Explosives} @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.a6bTH9RIOA1gwoza]{Grenade}&nbsp; @Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.tyqnHVNxWuUF1jDk]{EXP (Explosives)}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-weaponproperties.zgyP1fMQAonWXbqW]{(EXP) Flashbang}&nbsp;@Compendium[compendiums-mix-dnd5e.um5-rules.oaLjWnlYGoulu7oy]{Tech Level 1}</p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Also simply referred to as a stun grenade, a flash bang reduces the combat effectiveness of opponents by confusing and disorientating them with a sudden blinding magnesium flash and a deafening blast. The grenade body doesn't actually fragment so no shrapnel is dispersed.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text;\">Targets that fail the save are blinded and deafened until the end of your next turn.</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n<table class=\"NormalTable\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Flashbang </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Special </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Special </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">10 ft. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Â½ lb. </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">25 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">1 </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">No </span></td>\n<td width=\"200\"><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Detonator</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; color: #191813;\">&nbsp;</p>",
